  "description": {
    "zh": "来得真是时候，我的朋友。你有时间的话，帮我组一把枪吧。我的一个大客户要了把KRISS Vecto 9x19冲锋枪。他想要Mk.5 模块化导轨，Tactical Dynamics镂空前握把，你再给他配一个有效射程至少300米的瞄具，还要有至少33发容量的弹匣，以及一个消音器。人机功效高于50，后坐力低于230。谢谢！",
    "en": "Perfect timing, friend. If you have time, help me out with some gun customization. A major customer has placed an order for a KRISS Vector 9x19 submachine gun. He wants it to be equipped with an Mk.5 Modular Rail mount, Tactical Dynamics Skeletonized Foregrip, some iron sights or a scope with at least 300 meter sighting range, magazine with at least 33 rounds, and a silencer. Ergonomics over 50 and recoil under 230. Thanks!"
  },
